Post 3- @kkaran1m suggested a game which got me hooked and i am just waiting for the storyline to change, too much expectations i hope it's worth the time, anyone who has played? Comments me btao bhai

Post 4- A really SAD moment for me as our sunkissed series ended with it's episode 7 being released. The whole series gave me growth, new ideas and I'm definitely gonna score more, no stopping now!

Post 5- When you create a habit of eating good and healthy, these unnecessary cravings are waiting to take a leap and comw back so i couldn't just resist this time. Have been eating clean for 1.5 months now and no outside food enters my home now, feeling good psychologically let's see how long i can take this ahead 😛

Post 6- Kuch caption smjh ni ara to chodho
